e target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"foci in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the target is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This method has no effect if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userTrackingMode"},{"text":" property is set to a value","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"other than ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To specify a completion handler to execute after the animation finishes, use","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}]}]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)setTargetCoordinate:animated:","title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\